snippet.title: Bub's Big Blowout! - Sage 2023 Demo trailer
snippet.description:
This is an extended Sage 2023 demo trailer for Bub's Big Blowout! (my 3D Bubble Bobble fangame!)

Join Bub and his friends, as they brave a brand new 3D world! Use what you know from the 2D Bubble Bobble gameplay, to help you in this exciting new 3D adventure!

BUBBLE BOBBLE is owned by TAITO CORPORATION

THIS IS A NON PROFIT PROJECT!
